<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-10">
      <div class="panel panel-get-started">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <h1>Hi <%= "#{current_user.profile.first_name}!" %> We'd like to welcome you to Expercoin.</h1>
          <p>Since you are new, there are three ways to get started. Choose the role that describes you the best.</p>
          <a class="close-panel">&times</a>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <div class="body-block">
            <h3>As a Mentee (Buyer)</h3>
            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="text" class="form-control serch-offers" placeholder="Find Offers" />
            </div>
            <p>Popular searches</p>
          </div>
          <div class="body-block">
            <h3>As a Mentor (Seller)</h3>
            <div class="text-center">
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-md btn-md-lgr">Create your First Offer</button>
            </div>  
            <p>Your Offer is the service that you sell on Expercoin. Creating your Offer is an opportunity to show off your talent and provide buyers with all the information they need to help them decide to do business with</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-footer">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-md btn-md-lgr">Go to Dashboard</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>